xpadneo-dkms (0.10-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * New upstream release.
  * Drop redundant DKMS POST_INSTALL/POST_REMOVE hooks (fixes piuparts).
  * d/copyright: Update for upstream relicense of kernel module source
    to GPL-2.0-only and add CC0-1.0 for AppStream metainfo.
  * d/rules: Install upstream AppStream metainfo file.
  * d/patches: Fix AppStream component ID to use reverse-DNS format.
  * d/watch: Add Uversionmangle to handle upstream pre-release tags.

